"    You acknowledge that you have read this Policy and agree to all its terms and conditions. By accessing and using the Services and submitting your information you agree to be bound by this Policy. If you do not agree to abide by the terms of this Policy, you are not authorized to access or use the Services.\n This privacy policy was created with the help of the privacy policy generator at https://www.websitepolicies.com/privacy-policy-generator\n"

